verbose_text: In subjects without DM, absolute CD34 + cell level significantly increased 2.2-fold after hrG-CSF, whereas CD34 + cells completely failed to mobilize in DM patients (mean +/- SE change vs. baseline; non DM : 3,475 +/- 800 cells/mL; DM : 52 +/- 332 cells/mL; P = 5 x 10 -5) (XREF_FIG).
evidence: CD34 +  cell level significantly increased 2.2-fold after hrG-CSF, whereas CD34 +  cells completely failed to mobilize in DM
